******** How to enable remote debugging in android real device*******:

settings--->about phone--->build number seven time
then developer tab will appear--->usbdebugging


if above does not work then:
download oem usb driver based on device 

** how to use chrome debugging tool to inspect element in android real device ***:

in chrome browser click settings -->more tools--->inspect devices
refresh browser
make sure devices is connected

open url from mobile
click inspect
now u will see screen
click search
then get xpath